<br>
To anyone thinking of killing these with a wizard I recomend waiting tell you either have epic for a free 800 hp rune so you can sit and channel thru hits tell one dies.  Or wait tell you have strike of solusek so you can insta kill them before they can heal themselves.  From what I saw they have around 2500 hp.  So strike of solusek with some sort of inproved damage should be able to one shot kill them.  They hit slow but tend to hit for 50's 100's, and being a wizard you can only take so much of that.<br>
<br>
Yes I was able to kill them but not effectively enuff to make the time effort equal the reward.<br>
